  "instructions": [
    "1. Preheat oven to 400°F (200°C).",
    "2. Poach the fish in boiling water for 8-10 minutes, or until it's cooked through.",
    "3. Wrap the British wrap in foil and warm it in the oven for 2-3 minutes.",
    "4. Spread the silky mayonnaise on the wrap.",
    "5. Add the poached fish on top of the mayonnaise.",
    "6. Sprinkle the Italian seasoning on the fish.",
    "7. Squeeze the lemon juice on top of the fish.",
    "8. Add the chopped fresh parsley on top.",
    "9. Season with salt and black pepper to taste.",
    "10. Serve immediately."
